### Create a ticket
POST http://localhost:8080/tickets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_id": "CUST-DEMO-1",
  "customer_email": "demo@example.com",
  "customer_name": "Demo Customer",
  "subject": "Cannot access account",
  "description": "I cannot access my account after resetting the password.",
  "category": "account_access",
  "priority": "high",
  "status": "new",
  "assigned_to": "agent-demo",
  "tags": ["login", "demo"],
  "metadata": {"source": "web_form", "browser": "Chrome", "device_type": "desktop"}
}

### List tickets
GET http://localhost:8080/tickets

### Filter tickets
GET http://localhost:8080/tickets?category=account_access&priority=high&source=web_form

### Import CSV
POST http://localhost:8080/tickets/import
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=demo

--demo
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample_tickets.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

< ./sample_tickets.csv
--demo--

### Import JSON
POST http://localhost:8080/tickets/import
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=demo

--demo
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample_tickets.json"
Content-Type: application/json

< ./sample_tickets.json
--demo--

### Import XML
POST http://localhost:8080/tickets/import
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=demo

--demo
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample_tickets.xml"
Content-Type: application/xml

< ./sample_tickets.xml
--demo--
